text: First time tried the dry aged sashimi, to my surprise it was good. We had the sashimi platter and sushi various kinds. All the food is authentic and delicious. Not to mention  the green tea is fragrant.
amazing food! they have different takes on food im used to especially foods I've tried in Japan itself but they've outdone themselves! Will definitely come back.
Food is good. Kids enjoyed it very much. especially the chawanmushi, and the truffle rice. Kozen Pizza and Curry Katsu is good too. overall good experience.
The place had a really great vibe. We came for my brother's bday and the sushi cake was of course a unique highlight! Service was great too!
